* Iron Raptor shook her head at her friends and their antics, wondering if 
she could ever admit to the Maqximals that those two just happened to be her 
freinds.
But enough was enough about staying here while there was a battle back at 
base and giant machines coming this way bent on killing them.
Looking at Snow Tech and Shadow Cat as they moved off towards the base.
< Yes...they are.> she answered Prowl, even though she had sensed that the 
thought hadn't been directed to her.

Iron Raptor looked down at the curled little fuzz ball in her hands, simply 
them bringing him to the flat of her chest so that she had no possibility of 
droping him on the way to the battle. Looking up at Prowl as he tightens his 
hold on her, knowing that it was time to leave.
Returning the kiss he gave her as she felt her feet leave the ground, 
holding the piff ball to her a little more tightly.
< We had better, slag knows what's going on at the Cybertronian Fire.>
Iron Raptor squished herself against Prowl a little more, just not liking 
the idea of going fast...even though they had to.
But then a concern poped into her head. The little guy she held in her hands 
couldn't be in battle, but she couldn't just let him go.
She sighed, then looked down at him.*

" When we land, there is a compartment in my back armor, get into that, 
alright? And stay there."

* She then looked at Prowl.* < When we get to the CF, just drop me, I can 
land on my feet. I want to get into the fighting and get it over with as 
quick as I can. Alright?>
